# Grafana Monitor Skill

SSH로 EC2에 접속하여 3개 exporter에서 메트릭을 수집한다.

## Trigger Phrases

- "서버 상태 확인해줘", "메트릭 확인해줘", "서버 상태", "대시보드"
- "CPU/메모리 사용량", "JVM 상태"
- "응답시간 확인", "에러율 확인"

## 메트릭 수집 (Single SSH Session)

**항상 아래 명령어를 사용한다.** 개별 SSH 세션을 여러 번 열지 않는다.

```bash
EC2_HOST="${EC2_HOST:-52.79.56.222}"
EC2_SSH_PORT="${EC2_SSH_PORT:-2222}"
EC2_SSH_USER="${EC2_SSH_USER:-ec2-user}"
APP_ACTUATOR_PORT="${APP_ACTUATOR_PORT:-8081}"
NODE_EXPORTER_PORT="${NODE_EXPORTER_PORT:-9100}"
MYSQL_EXPORTER_PORT="${MYSQL_EXPORTER_PORT:-9104}"
ssh -i /root/.ssh/ec2-key.pem -o StrictHostKeyChecking=no -p "$EC2_SSH_PORT" -o ConnectTimeout=5 "${EC2_SSH_USER}@${EC2_HOST}" \
  "APP_ACTUATOR_PORT=${APP_ACTUATOR_PORT} NODE_EXPORTER_PORT=${NODE_EXPORTER_PORT} MYSQL_EXPORTER_PORT=${MYSQL_EXPORTER_PORT} bash -s" <<'REMOTE_SCRIPT'
echo "=== ACTUATOR HEALTH ==="
curl -s "http://localhost:${APP_ACTUATOR_PORT}/actuator/health"

echo ""
echo "=== SPRING BOOT METRICS ==="
curl -s "http://localhost:${APP_ACTUATOR_PORT}/actuator/prometheus" | grep -E "^(http_server_requests_seconds_(count|sum)|tomcat_threads|hikaricp_connections_(active|max)|jvm_memory_(used|max)_bytes.*heap|jvm_gc_pause|cache_gets_total)" | grep -v "#"

echo ""
echo "=== NODE METRICS ==="
curl -s "http://localhost:${NODE_EXPORTER_PORT}/metrics" | grep -E "^(node_memory_(MemAvailable|MemTotal|SwapFree|SwapTotal)_bytes |node_load(1|5|15) |node_filesystem_(avail|size)_bytes.*fstype=\"xfs\"|node_disk_io_time|node_network_(receive|transmit)_bytes_total.*eth0|node_time_seconds |node_boot_time_seconds |node_filefd)" | grep -v "#" | grep -v tmpfs

echo ""
echo "=== MYSQL METRICS ==="
curl -s "http://localhost:${MYSQL_EXPORTER_PORT}/metrics" | grep -E "^mysql_global_(status_(threads_connected|queries|slow_queries|innodb_buffer_pool_read|innodb_row_lock|threads_created|connections|table_locks_waited|aborted_connects)|variables_max_connections) " | grep -v "#"
REMOTE_SCRIPT
```

## 메트릭 해석

- **Gauge** (예: `node_load1 0.5`): 현재 값, 그대로 사용
- **Counter** (예: `mysql_global_status_queries 71544`): 누적 값, 반드시 "(누적)"으로 표기

## Severity Thresholds

| Metric | WARN | CRITICAL |
|--------|------|----------|
| CPU (Load Avg, 1 vCPU) | > 1.0 | > 2.0 |
| Memory | > 80% | > 95% |
| Swap | > 50% | > 80% |
| JVM Heap | > 80% | > 95% |
| DB Connection (HikariCP) | > 70% | > 90% |
| Tomcat Thread | > 70% | > 90% |
| Disk Usage | > 80% | > 90% |

Overall severity = highest individual severity.
